&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve uploaded a revised version of the reverted patch at &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/41691&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/41691&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

